1747
01:27:21.236 --> 01:27:23.672
Nice. nice. nice. okay.

1748
01:27:26.174 --> 01:27:28.811
<i>Pull over.</i>
<i>You have been surrounded.</i>

1749
01:27:28.844 --> 01:27:30.145
