- Until this very moment.

1882
01:37:05.820 --> 01:37:07.755
Charlie Vanderberg!

1883
01:37:11.093 --> 01:37:12.928
- Wow.
- Whoo!

1884
01:37:16.264 --> 01:37:18.266
